buildCommand: cd frontend && pnpm install --frozen-lockfile && pnpm run build
ignoreCommand: if [ -z "$VERCEL_GIT_PREVIOUS_SHA" ]; then exit 1; fi; if ! git cat-file -e "$VERCEL_GIT_PREVIOUS_SHA" 2>/dev/null; then git fetch origin "$VERCEL_GIT_PREVIOUS_SHA":"$VERCEL_GIT_PREVIOUS_SHA" --depth=1 || git fetch --unshallow; fi; git diff --quiet "$VERCEL_GIT_PREVIOUS_SHA" "$VERCEL_GIT_COMMIT_SHA" -- frontend/
